      "text": [
        " خَالِطِ النَّاسَ تَخْبُرْهُمْ وَ مَتَى تَخْبُرْهُمْ تَقْلِهِمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "<a id=\"_Toc492473320\">H 14644</a> – A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Al-Hajjaal, from hammaad, from Al-Halby, who has narrated the following:",
          "<span class=\"first-chapter-phrase\"><span class=\"first-in-chapter character-a\">A</span>bu Abdullah</span><sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Intermingle with the people to find out about them, and when you find out about them, (only then) travel/associate with them’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "196. A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Al-Hajjaal, from hammaad, from Al-Halby, who has narrated the following: Abu Abdullah (a.s.) said: ‘Intermingle with the people to find out about them, and when you find out about them, (only then) travel/associate with them’."
        ]
      }
